A school district has been ordered to pay $ 225,000 to three girls who were bullied into sending nude pictures to a boy at their middle school .
It marks the end of a six-year case , after the teenagers first reported reported to officials at Clatskanie Middle School in Oregon - only to be told to ` suck it up .
Josi Harrison , Laura Lefebvre , and Hailey Walden claim their high school-age boyfriends lured them into sending naked pictures to their phones .
On Thursday , they ordered that each girl receive $ 75,000 in damages .